<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Abhiruchii Restaurant | Best Biryani in Chirala</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
body{font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;background:#FFF8E7;color:#333;scroll-behavior:smooth}

nav{
position:fixed;
width:100%;
background:rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
padding:15px 40px;
display:flex;
justify-content:space-between;
align-items:center;
color:white;
z-index:1000
}

nav a{
color:white;
text-decoration:none;
margin-left:20px;
font-weight:500;
}

.hero{
height:100vh;
background:linear-gradient(rgba(139,0,0,0.7),rgba(139,0,0,0.7)),
url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1604908177522-432c26f0d48e');
background-size:cover;
background-position:center;
display:flex;
flex-direction:column;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
color:white;
text-align:center;
padding:20px;
}

.hero h1{font-size:3.5rem;margin-bottom:20px}
.hero p{font-size:1.2rem;margin-bottom:30px}

.btn{
background:#FF6B00;
color:white;
padding:14px 35px;
border:none;
border-radius:30px;
cursor:pointer;
text-decoration:none;
font-weight:600;
transition:0.3s
}

.btn:hover{background:#e65c00;transform:scale(1.05)}

.section{padding:100px 20px;text-align:center}

.section h2{
font-size:2.5rem;
margin-bottom:20px;
color:#8B0000
}

.cards{
display:flex;
flex-wrap:wrap;
justify-content:center;
gap:30px;
margin-top:40px
}

.card{
background:white;
width:300px;
border-radius:15px;
overflow:hidden;
box-shadow:0 15px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
transition:0.3s
}

.card img{
width:100%;
height:200px;
object-fit:cover
}

.card-content{
padding:20px
}

.card:hover{
transform:translateY(-15px)
}

.cta{
background:#8B0000;
color:white;
padding:80px 20px;
text-align:center
}

.cta h2{font-size:2.5rem;margin-bottom:20px}

.footer{
background:#1A1A1A;
color:white;
padding:40px;
text-align:center
}

@media(max-width:768px){
.hero h1{font-size:2.2rem}
.section h2{font-size:1.8rem}
.cards{flex-direction:column;align-items:center}
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<nav>
<div><strong>Abhiruchii</strong></div>
<div>
<a href="#menu">Menu</a>
<a href="#about">About</a>
<a href="#contact">Contact</a>
</div>
</nav>

<div class="hero">
<h1>Authentic Andhra Flavours</h1>
<p>Spicy. Fresh. Unforgettable.</p>
<a href="tel:08594239907" class="btn">Call & Reserve Now</a>
</div>

<div id="menu" class="section">
<h2>Signature Dishes</h2>
<div class="cards">

<div class="card">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1589302168068-964664d93dc0" alt="Chicken Biryani">
<div class="card-content">
<h3>Chicken Biryani</h3>
<p>Bold Andhra spices with rich aroma.</p>
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1625943553852-781c6dd46faa" alt="Mutton Biryani">
<div class="card-content">
<h3>Mutton Biryani</h3>
<p>Slow-cooked perfection with authentic flavor.</p>
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1604908812640-6aab8f94cfe1" alt="Chilli Chicken">
<div class="card-content">
<h3>Chilli Chicken</h3>
<p>The spicy starter everyone loves.</p>
</div>
</div>

</div>
</div>

<div id="about" class="section">
<h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
<p>✔ 7,000+ Happy Customers</p>
<p>✔ Budget Friendly (₹200–400)</p>
<p>✔ Prime Location in Chirala</p>
<p>✔ Fast Service</p>
</div>

<div class="cta">
<h2>Ready to Experience Real Andhra Spice?</h2>
<a href="tel:08594239907" class="btn">Book Your Table</a>
</div>

<div id="contact" class="footer">
<p>Second Floor, JKC Complex, Andhra Ratna Rd, Chirala</p>
<p>Open Till 10:30 PM</p>
<p>© 2026 Abhiruchii Restaurant</p>
</div>

</body>
</html>
